title: Dov Davidoff
description: DOV DAVIDOFF (comedian! actor! writer! one of the most interesting people ever! cool guy!) is one of Pete's favorite YMIW guests ever: open, funny, thoughtful, badass. Good lord this is a great one. I don't want to even spoil anything here. Just get into it, you weirdos! It was the best. WHAT WAS IT, THE BEST? Yes. Just yes.
